[
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "25963349780572399",
    "like_count": 16,
    "media_id": "77806737388282410",
    "parent_id": "17984221056330712",
    "text": "Copper found the armadillo again. Caught him mid-standoff in the yard. Eddie won't believe it.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-27T16:06:30+00:00",
    "user_id": "80210740717894326",
    "username": "kai.osborne"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "82292061557835652",
    "like_count": 20,
    "media_id": "27959698596074886",
    "parent_id": "17902336718450091",
    "text": "That's Copper last Tuesday, caught him mid-yawn. Lazy old dog.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-26T21:32:32+00:00",
    "user_id": "36253699656530132",
    "username": "dorothy.osborne"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "81366181092753593",
    "like_count": 25,
    "media_id": "18101024471578966",
    "parent_id": "17865490223107744",
    "text": "Sent that one to Kai too. Copper photobombed the whole thing, classic.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-27T09:56:17+00:00",
    "user_id": "15110835330836447",
    "username": "ben.osborne"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "62859057175166411",
    "like_count": 11,
    "media_id": "30714325092068339",
    "parent_id": "17819045662208913",
    "text": "Is that Copper on your bench? That's the leather you set aside for the commission.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-25T04:54:24+00:00",
    "user_id": "80815338544893009",
    "username": "angela.ruiz.gallery"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "99157741506106307",
    "like_count": 2,
    "media_id": "72114437738450462",
    "parent_id": "17773910448506182",
    "text": "Sent you that pic of Copper on the porch. Kai took it last Sunday. She's got a good eye.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-23T23:02:53+00:00",
    "user_id": "60524647997483089",
    "username": "martha.york"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "49172235600832263",
    "like_count": 19,
    "media_id": "95208376296422983",
    "parent_id": "17728375334607461",
    "text": "That bolo turned out clean. The coral reads warm against the sterling. Good pick.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-26T12:45:31+00:00",
    "user_id": "26502373785794177",
    "username": "rita.benally"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "60489319836089927",
    "like_count": 25,
    "media_id": "12844091703736899",
    "parent_id": "17682940220708350",
    "text": "That Royston slab cut clean. Send it back over when the cuff is done. Want to see it.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-25T02:58:05+00:00",
    "user_id": "31925736000666928",
    "username": "eddie.tsosie"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "80631171778080715",
    "like_count": 17,
    "media_id": "99440915184552536",
    "parent_id": "17637504106809249",
    "text": "Just saw the buckle. That can't be the same stamps. They cut sharper than mine ever did.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-26T14:42:15+00:00",
    "user_id": "30960758555742481",
    "username": "thomas.kee"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "90531984860884719",
    "like_count": 18,
    "media_id": "46085799422953712",
    "parent_id": "17592068992910148",
    "text": "That shot of Copper and me from the Gallup parade. Dog looked better than me.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-25T10:33:35+00:00",
    "user_id": "26442863538872503",
    "username": "thomas.kee"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "82976445672941434",
    "like_count": 5,
    "media_id": "10089674090708589",
    "parent_id": "17546633879011047",
    "text": "Got the photo. Copper photobombed the whole shot but I think it works. Might frame it for the shop.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-23T06:01:09+00:00",
    "user_id": "94570550794063366",
    "username": "thomas.kee.stone"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "46067552035935494",
    "like_count": 15,
    "media_id": "98167308609274100",
    "parent_id": "17501197765111946",
    "text": "Sent you the photo from Copper's morning walk. That dog's happier in Gallup than I've ever been.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-20T16:53:23+00:00",
    "user_id": "93975240573429350",
    "username": "eddie.tsosie.shop"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "51969857319533638",
    "like_count": 18,
    "media_id": "55322479749930798",
    "parent_id": "17455761651212845",
    "text": "That shot of the Gallup skyline you sent is something. Going up on the shop wall.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-22T06:50:39+00:00",
    "user_id": "39532019386093402",
    "username": "martha.york.skies"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "47024120593528772",
    "like_count": 18,
    "media_id": "57331998002687675",
    "parent_id": "17410325537313744",
    "text": "Got your pic. That turquoise slab's the cleanest I've seen come through Gallup in a while.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-16T06:04:22+00:00",
    "user_id": "47124183147730736",
    "username": "eddie.tsosie.supply"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "28762473267026135",
    "like_count": 6,
    "media_id": "27458842461993322",
    "parent_id": "17364890423414643",
    "text": "That Copper or a bear. Hard to tell with the hat on him, but it counts as a morale boost so here we are.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-24T10:42:32+00:00",
    "user_id": "30760423031016153",
    "username": "ben.osborne.garage"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "24289718292755341",
    "like_count": 9,
    "media_id": "37663291646318957",
    "parent_id": "17319454309515542",
    "text": "That's my kid. Didn't realize she had that much daylight on the pack. Send that one over.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-25T20:50:03+00:00",
    "user_id": "90323273859705622",
    "username": "rita.benally.coach"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "33186052471829940",
    "like_count": 14,
    "media_id": "83920174655028341",
    "parent_id": "17274018195616441",
    "text": "That cuff turned out clean. The spiny oyster reads warmer than I expected against the sterling. Good call on the stone.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-12T18:40:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "47124183147730736",
    "username": "eddie.tsosie.supply"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "70912348556037128",
    "like_count": 22,
    "media_id": "77806737388282410",
    "parent_id": "17228582081717340",
    "text": "Dad your bolo sold at the Santa Fe booth before noon. Lady drove from Sedona for it. Told you the coral inlay would go.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-28T01:18:47+00:00",
    "user_id": "80210740717894326",
    "username": "kai.osborne"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "58473019228764501",
    "like_count": 8,
    "media_id": "27959698596074886",
    "parent_id": "17183145967818249",
    "text": "Sunday call still on? Want to hear about the buckle order before the craft fair. Bring the photos.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-26T23:11:05+00:00",
    "user_id": "36253699656530132",
    "username": "dorothy.osborne"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "61029847735518290",
    "like_count": 12,
    "media_id": "18101024471578966",
    "parent_id": "17137709853919148",
    "text": "Pop taught you that stamp work and it shows. He would've kept this one for himself.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-27T13:27:39+00:00",
    "user_id": "15110835330836447",
    "username": "ben.osborne"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "49583012267904815",
    "like_count": 7,
    "media_id": "30714325092068339",
    "parent_id": "17092273740020047",
    "text": "The cuff you set for me holds up at work all week. No scratches yet. Worth every dollar.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-25T09:14:52+00:00",
    "user_id": "26502373785794177",
    "username": "rita.benally"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "30715948261037744",
    "like_count": 13,
    "media_id": "72114437738450462",
    "parent_id": "17046837626121946",
    "text": "Pulled the Royston rough you asked about. Heading west to Red Rock tomorrow, will bring it by the shop.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-24T08:43:18+00:00",
    "user_id": "31925736000666928",
    "username": "eddie.tsosie"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "82046137759028461",
    "like_count": 10,
    "media_id": "95208376296422983",
    "parent_id": "17001401512222845",
    "text": "Got the silver shipment in. Half-hard sterling sheet and the round wire you wanted. Invoice is on the bench by the rolls.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-23T15:36:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "47124183147730736",
    "username": "eddie.tsosie.supply"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "59371028846650193",
    "like_count": 19,
    "media_id": "12844091703736899",
    "parent_id": "16955965398323744",
    "text": "Kai placed third at the meet in the Zuni Mountains 5K. Held her pace the whole back half. Proud of that kid.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-21T19:52:41+00:00",
    "user_id": "94570550794063366",
    "username": "thomas.kee.stone"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "30948576201837465",
    "like_count": 4,
    "media_id": "99440915184552536",
    "parent_id": "16910529284424643",
    "text": "Gallery in Sedona wants two more cuffs by the winter show. Let them know when the bench clears.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-22T21:09:14+00:00",
    "user_id": "30960758555742481",
    "username": "thomas.kee"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "47502938176450382",
    "like_count": 11,
    "media_id": "46085799422953712",
    "parent_id": "16865093170525542",
    "text": "Dropped the coral off at the studio. Spiny oyster's in the same box. Square up the tab Sunday.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-20T11:48:30+00:00",
    "user_id": "26442863538872503",
    "username": "thomas.kee"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "61847029358104627",
    "like_count": 9,
    "media_id": "10089674090708589",
    "parent_id": "16819657056626441",
    "text": "The bolo for the gallery is ready when you are. Photos look good, weight feels right in hand.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-19T17:31:56+00:00",
    "user_id": "39532019386093402",
    "username": "martha.york.skies"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "30659174820593817",
    "like_count": 6,
    "media_id": "98167308609274100",
    "parent_id": "16774220942727340",
    "text": "That belt buckle you stamped came out sharp. Wore it to the alumni thing and didn't shut up about it.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-18T20:25:43+00:00",
    "user_id": "30760423031016153",
    "username": "ben.osborne.garage"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "58013947726508194",
    "like_count": 15,
    "media_id": "55322479749930798",
    "parent_id": "16728784828828249",
    "text": "Kai left her spikes at practice again. I've got them. No more Creedence on the drive until she remembers.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-17T22:14:09+00:00",
    "user_id": "90323273859705622",
    "username": "rita.benally.coach"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "47629185503718264",
    "like_count": 8,
    "media_id": "57331998002687675",
    "parent_id": "16683348714929148",
    "text": "The turquoise you hand-cut for the shop order shipped. Buyer in Albuquerque already left five stars.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-15T18:07:22+00:00",
    "user_id": "47124183147730736",
    "username": "eddie.tsosie.supply"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "30187456209374851",
    "like_count": 21,
    "media_id": "83920174655028341",
    "parent_id": "16637912601030047",
    "text": "Pop's old stamps still cut true. Did the feather pattern on this buckle with his tools. Felt right.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-13T16:33:48+00:00",
    "user_id": "15110835330836447",
    "username": "ben.osborne"
  }
]